  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/262810/extras/74747ec2e516523d6ba9d3c3063f3230.poster.avif?t=1768395322\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/262810/extras/74747ec2e516523d6ba9d3c3063f3230.webm?t=1768395322\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/262810/extras/74747ec2e516523d6ba9d3c3063f3230.mp4?t=1768395322\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >UBER-FAST</h2>Rapid and unforgiving gameplay where you will run away from hazards and combat monsters.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >TURBO-RANDOM</h2>Every level is generated, every situation is unique.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SUPER-DEEP</h2>A plenty of heroes to lead and tons of weapons to fire.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/262810/extras/faaefb2f457a7b8090728af1d01ca363.poster.avif?t=1768395322\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/262810/extras/faaefb2f457a7b8090728af1d01ca363.webm?t=1768395322\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/262810/extras/faaefb2f457a7b8090728af1d01ca363.mp4?t=1768395322\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>So, your beloved superiors have just landed you, by mistake, on a home world of every monster, virus and hazard in our galaxy. Time is running out before you either burn or, worse, become one of them. Lead a squad of hardcore space marines and mercenaries through the hell made by the devoted fans of DOOM and ALIEN.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/262810/extras/22290453e6df4244edfb77b4bbcd481f.poster.avif?t=1768395322\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/262810/extras/22290453e6df4244edfb77b4bbcd481f.webm?t=1768395322\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/262810/extras/22290453e6df4244edfb77b4bbcd481f.mp4?t=1768395322\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/262810/extras/74747ec2e516523d6ba9d3c3063f3230.poster.avif?t=1768395322\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/262810/extras/74747ec2e516523d6ba9d3c3063f3230.webm?t=1768395322\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/262810/extras/74747ec2e516523d6ba9d3c3063f3230.mp4?t=1768395322\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >UBER-FAST</h2>Rapid and unforgiving gameplay where you will run away from hazards and combat monsters.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >TURBO-RANDOM</h2>Every level is generated, every situation is unique.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SUPER-DEEP</h2>A plenty of heroes to lead and tons of weapons to fire.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/262810/extras/faaefb2f457a7b8090728af1d01ca363.poster.avif?t=1768395322\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/262810/extras/faaefb2f457a7b8090728af1d01ca363.webm?t=1768395322\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/262810/extras/faaefb2f457a7b8090728af1d01ca363.mp4?t=1768395322\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>So, your beloved superiors have just landed you, by mistake, on a home world of every monster, virus and hazard in our galaxy. Time is running out before you either burn or, worse, become one of them. Lead a squad of hardcore space marines and mercenaries through the hell made by the devoted fans of DOOM and ALIEN.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/262810/extras/22290453e6df4244edfb77b4bbcd481f.poster.avif?t=1768395322\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/262810/extras/22290453e6df4244edfb77b4bbcd481f.webm?t=1768395322\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/262810/extras/22290453e6df4244edfb77b4bbcd481f.mp4?t=1768395322\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
